data.description: Welcome to this delightful, move-in ready ranch with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths a 2-car garage, and approximately 1,764 sf.  A wall of windows grace the living room and provide an incredible amount of natural light. You'll love the separate dining room, updated kitchen with stainless appliances and an adjoining hearth room with wood burning fireplace. Radiant heat in the floors throughout. The primary suite is large and spacious with warm wood floors, a wood accent wall, two closets, and a private bath. Fall weather is the perfect time to enjoy the attached sunroom and outdoor space complete with a fenced and level backyard, pergola, outdoor fire pit and large patio area. The 2-car garage leads to the mudroom plus an additional finished storage/office space.  Brand new roof in 2023. All kitchen appliances stay as well as the garage refrigerator. Conveniently located near restaurants, shopping, and schools.
